_sText:
UPDATES (VERSION 2)

- New Skybox (Purple, more atmospheric, better?).
- Fixed FPS issue in the corner next to A-Site Vent.
- Fixed Floor Glitch in Mid (infront of mid 'garden'.
- Fixed Shadow glitch on the N of the 'KNA' factory logo.
- Added Biohazard tanks (FROM CS:GO) to fill the empty space.
- Opened up the backyard area under watch tower, AWP gap is possible.
- Added Caged-Sides to the Lobby next to CT spawn ( adds extra protection from people playing mid CT side).
- Fixed roof exploit on the H-shaped mid section.
- Fixed roof exploit on bridged bomb site.
- Changed tall box on A site to Yellow cannister, slightly taller requires a tad more effort to get onto.
- Made the A-Site Upper Door Fixed Open, for ease of access and escape.
- Fixed unrealistic looking point in one of the background cliffs
- Added tree outside CT Spawn building to provide more cover during rotates between A and B. It also looks nice.
